## Commands
- `make setup` — Initialize environment
- `make lint` — Lint check
- `make format` — Auto format
- `make typecheck` — Type check
- `make test` — Run tests
- `make check` — Full check (lint + typecheck + test)
{% if needs_server -%}
- `make dev` — Start dev server
- `make test-e2e` — End-to-end test
{% endif -%}

